kv5.10:3.3_0: Atthi sāvakassa khandhapaññatti āyatanapaññatti dhātupaññatti saccapaññatti indriyapaññatti puggalapaññattīti?
kv5.10:4.3_0: Sāvako jino satthā sammāsambuddho sabbaññū sabbadassāvī dhammassāmī dhammappaṭisaraṇoti?
kv5.10:5.3_0: Sāvako anuppannassa maggassa uppādetā asañjātassa maggassa sañjanetā anakkhātassa maggassa akkhātā maggaññū maggavidū maggakovidoti?
kv5.10:6.6_0: tena hi sāvakassa phale ñāṇaṁ atthīti …pe….
kv5.10:7.1_0: Vimuttiñāṇaṁ vimuttaṁ, sekhassa asekhaṁ ñāṇaṁ, viparīte ñāṇaṁ,
kv5.10:7.1_1: aniyatassa niyāmagamanāya atthi ñāṇaṁ, sabbaṁ ñāṇaṁ paṭisambhidāti, sammutiñāṇaṁ, cetopariyāye ñāṇaṁ, anāgate ñāṇaṁ, paṭuppanne ñāṇaṁ, sāvakassa phale ñāṇanti.
kv5.10:8.1_0: Sattupaladdhiṁ, upaharato, balaṁ, gihi’ssa arahā ca, vimuttipañcamanti.
